+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: Node.js
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: none
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: npx cucumber-js --dry-run
+- focused: npx cucumber-js features/{scenario}.feature --name "{Scenario Name}" --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"
+- broad: npx cucumber-js features/ --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"
+- coverage: none
+- step-usage: npx cucumber-js --dry-run --format summary
+- plank-inventory: none
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: none
+- conformance: none
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: @logic - pure local tests, no external accounts. Fast, deterministic, safe.
+- weather: none
+- runrecord: none
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: locked
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
